It's easy to be a Christian.

00:20:55.600 --> 00:20:55.876
It's easy to make it in the rapture.

00:20:56.151 --> 00:20:58.920
It's called a personal relationship with the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:20:58.920 --> 00:21:01.790
It's not about works, lest any man should boast.

00:21:01.790 --> 00:21:02.720
It's about grace.

00:21:02.720 --> 00:21:04.503
It's about the grace of God.

00:21:20.213 --> 00:21:20.547
And it's about walking your salvation out with fear and trembling.

00:21:20.547 --> 00:21:27.071
It's about seeking Him daily and having intimacy with Jesus Christ.

00:21:38.160 --> 00:21:38.560
And so I just want—if you don't have that, you say, 'I don't have any of those things'—well, this is how you start.

00:21:38.560 --> 00:21:41.943
This is the opening of the door to Christianity.

00:21:41.943 --> 00:21:43.830
Say this prayer after me.

00:21:43.830 --> 00:21:45.210
Say, 'Jesus, I'm a sinner.

00:21:48.426 --> 00:21:55.577
I come to you and I want you to be my Lord and my Savior.

00:21:55.577 --> 00:21:58.720
Write my name in the Lamb's Book of Life.

00:21:58.720 --> 00:21:59.726
I'm a sinner.

00:22:12.520 --> 00:22:12.790
Lord, forgive me.

00:22:12.790 --> 00:22:15.839
Forgive me for all that I've done wrong.

00:22:15.839 --> 00:22:17.710
' You're confessing your sins.

00:22:17.710 --> 00:22:21.120
'Forgive me, Lord, for murder, for whatever it may be.

00:22:21.120 --> 00:22:25.760
' Nothing is too big for God to forgive—adultery, murder, fornication, or gossip.

00:22:25.760 --> 00:22:28.023
God, I thank you that you forgive me.

00:22:28.023 --> 00:22:30.343
Just tell Him, 'Forgive me, Lord.

00:22:30.343 --> 00:22:35.189
Forgive me.

00:22:35.189 --> 00:22:40.068
Cleanse me with your blood from all unrighteousness.

00:22:40.068 --> 00:22:43.280
' Father, I thank you, Lord.

00:22:43.280 --> 00:22:46.387
You cleanse me from all unrighteousness.

00:22:46.387 --> 00:22:50.046
Write my name in that Lamb's Book of Life.

00:23:01.840 --> 00:23:02.120
And Father, I thank you.

00:23:13.831 --> 00:23:14.088
I make you my Lord and my Savior.

00:23:14.088 --> 00:23:20.423
I believe that you died on the cross for me and you rose again on the third day.

00:23:23.560 --> 00:23:24.053
You just believe it.

00:23:24.053 --> 00:23:26.586
I believe that you forgave me.

00:23:26.586 --> 00:23:27.360
It's easy.

00:23:39.810 --> 00:23:40.080
We make salvation too hard.

00:23:40.080 --> 00:23:45.919
We make it into something that it's, 'I've got to do all this.

00:23:45.919 --> 00:23:46.819
' No.

00:23:46.819 --> 00:23:49.760
Jesus already paid the price for it, folks.

00:24:04.160 --> 00:24:04.400
He paid the price for you to be free.

00:24:07.428 --> 00:24:07.793
Just say, 'I've confessed my sins.

00:24:07.793 --> 00:24:08.751
Forgive me.

00:24:08.751 --> 00:24:09.936
I'm a sinner.

00:24:09.936 --> 00:24:11.484
I need you now.

00:24:11.484 --> 00:24:17.126
' Father, after I've done that, I thank you that I'm yours.

00:24:17.126 --> 00:24:18.949
I'm adopted into your home.

00:24:18.949 --> 00:24:26.427
He adopts you, he washes you up, he cleanses you, and he cleans you all up.

00:24:26.427 --> 00:24:31.579
'Holy Spirit, I invite you inside of me.

00:24:31.579 --> 00:24:32.660
Wall to wall.

00:24:32.660 --> 00:24:35.439
Holy Ghost, free me from all kinds of satanic bondage.

00:24:35.439 --> 00:24:36.159
I'm free.

00:24:36.159 --> 00:24:41.679
' The Bible says, 'Whom the Son has set free is free indeed.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
' So, He sets you free and you're free indeed.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
I'm not bound by any kind of devil anymore.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
I'm set free by the blood of the Lamb.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
And so you just believe that.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
Confess with your mouth.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
Believe in your heart that Jesus is your Lord and Savior and you're saved.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
Now, go to church.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
Find a church that believes in the baptism of the Holy Spirit.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
Find a church that believes in water baptism.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Get baptized.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.700
Go and declare your salvation to the world—declare what you've done to the world—that Jesus is your Lord and Savior by baptism.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
Go and do that.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
Find a church that does that and get excited about the word.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
I just want to encourage you all.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
It's not hard to get saved.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.050
Get a Bible.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
Download it on your phone if you don't have one.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
Start reading your Bible every day and ask the Holy Spirit.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.550
Say, 'Holy Spirit, make this word real to me according to Ephesians 1:18.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.050
' Remember that the eyes of your understanding would be enlightened that you may know the hope of His calling on my life.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.050
'What is it?

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
Let the eyes of the understanding—the word—become real to me that it's not confusing.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
' Pray over your mind.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
'I understand what I read.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
' And just feed on the word of God daily.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Pray daily.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
Seek Him, Jesus, and be real with Him.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.050
Don't be religious.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
You don't have to be religious.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
'Jesus, how are you today?

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
How's your day today?

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
I had a rough day today.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
I need you to give me strength.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
' Again, you're not going to be perfect overnight.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.750
Just like a child, you learn how to walk, you fall when you walk, you get up, brush yourself off, and you walk some more.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
That's the same way it is to be saved.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.600
You fall, you get back up, brush yourself off, you keep walking it out by faith.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
That's how we live the Christian life.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
We're all a work in progress.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
Even me, I don't have it all together.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:10.150
Even with how far I feel like I am with the Lord some days, then you have days that you go, 'Man, I've got a long way to go.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
' That's called humility.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
You just keep yourself humble before the Lord.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.600
Humble yourself underneath the mighty hand of the Lord, and in time, He will exalt you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
So, I just want to say I love you all.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.350
I pray that if you got born again today, please comment down below if you gave your heart to Jesus Christ.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Tell somebody.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
Be excited about it.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.600
It's an exciting time—a transfer from the old man to a new man, being born again.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
I hope this blessed you all watching this video today.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
God bless you all and thank you for watching.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Bye-bye.
